# Logger Specification

This specification describes the behavior of the Logger class.

## Logger should be created with a name
* Create a logger with name "test"
* Logger name should be "test"

## Logger should log messages
* Create a logger with name "app"
* Log message "Test message"
* Logger should have 1 messages

## Logger should clear messages
* Create a logger with name "app"
* Log message "Message 1"
* Log message "Message 2"
* Clear all messages
* Logger should have 0 messages
